channel.title: Don’t Toy With Me, Miss Nagatoro
channel.description: When an introverted male student meets a sadistic freshman girl named Nagatoro, his life is turned upside down. She first quietly observes his reaction to verbal abuse from some other high-school girls that are not well-meaning, realizes that oddly enough in his case it may be exactly what he needs, and so begins a sequence of her teasing him. It soon becomes increasingly obvious (to the reader, not to him) that her teasing is actually sardonic, well-intentioned, and flirtatious, in between the bullying and teasing, something else begins to blossom. A lovey-dovey(…?) story between a shy nerd and an S-Dere (Sadistic Tsundere) begins.
